          Tu empresa formal y 100% <span class="text-accent">legal con Constival.</span>
        </h1>
        
        <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-balance text-lg text-white/80 md:text-xl lg:mx-0">
          Hacemos que la constitución de tu SAS sea rápida y segura. Protegemos tu patrimonio con estatutos a medida, sin burocracia y con asesoría experta permanente.
        </p>
      
        <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col items-center gap-4 sm:flex-row lg:justify-start">
          <a href="/crear-sas-ecuador" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg btn-pill shadow-xl shadow-accent/20">
            Crear mi empresa hoy
          </a>
          <a href="#precios" class="text-white/80 hover:text-white flex items-center gap-2 font-semibold transition-colors py-3 px-6">
            Ver planes y tarifas
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
       -->

      <!-- Right Side - Service Cards Slider -->
      <div 
        class="carousel overflow-hidden -mx-6 lg:mx-0 lg:absolute lg:right-0 lg:w-[60%] lg:top-1/2 lg:-translate-y-1/2"
      >
        <InfiniteSlider speed={40} gap={24} pauseOnHover={true}>
          {services.map((service) => (
            <ServiceCard 
              title={service.title}
              description={service.description}
              icon={service.icon}
              variant={service.variant}
            />
          ))}
        </InfiniteSlider>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* Decorative glow animation */
  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% {
      opacity: 0.2;
      transform: scale(1);
    }
    50% {
      opacity: 0.3;
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }
  }
  
  .animate-pulse {
    animation: pulse 4s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
</style>
